.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[264,1324,284,950]" box="[312,1254,924,950]" pageId="3" pageNumber="4">
Etymology.­ The species name, 
<taxonomicName box="[687,840,924,949]" class="Insecta" family="Colobathristidae" genus="Trichocentrus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ecuatorianus">
